; Test value and year directives through general_directive
; Covers textual_directives.cc lines 896-900

value market(amount, date, "$")

year 2023

01/15 Test
    Expenses:Food    $50.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg
23-Jan-15 Test                  Expenses:Food                $50.00       $50.00
                                Assets:Cash                 $-50.00            0
end test
